These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: whist, poker
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, november
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, tulip
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, cauliflower
1. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Game       | poker       | whist |
| Birthday         | november | january  |
| Flower       | tulip    | aconite    |
| Food   | cauliflower       | asparagus      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, cranberry
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, august
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, traveling
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, purple
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Food      | cranberry     | cucumber |
| Birthday           | april | august      |
| Hobby   | traveling  | camping      |
| Color         | orange | purple     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, architect
City: venice, hannover
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, march
House: palace, wooden
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the architect##1
2. the dancer is the wooden house##1
3. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Job      | dancer | architect  |
| City          | venice    | hannover   |
| Birthday   | march  | june   |
| House     | wooden     | palace |

