.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, woodworking
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, december
House: gothic-revival, tower
1. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Hobby      | gardening       | woodworking |
| Pet          | frog         | goldfish    |
| Birthday           | december | september    |
| House   | gothic-revival           | tower   |

