.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-6::.
2 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bongani
There are 2 different nationalities: german, spanish
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, airplane
1. the german is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Pet      | ferret      | mouse       |
| Cigar   | aristoff | bongani    |
| Nationality   | german    | spanish        |
| Transport         | airplane    | train |

