.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-9::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, purple
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, marigold
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, zombie
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, punk
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Color   | black         | purple    |
| Flower       | marigold     | daisy  |
| Movie-Genre      | action | zombie     |
| Music-Genre        | punk     | salsa |

