.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
House: farmhouse, cape-cod
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, watermelon
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, blend
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, tennis
1. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| House           | cape-cod | farmhouse     |
| Food   | cabbage          | watermelon |
| Cigar           | bluemaster          | blend    |
| Sport     | tennis            | surfing       |

 